title.narrative: Trade: Recognised Seasonal Employer (RSE) Worker Training Programme

description.narrative: The Recognised Seasonal Employers' (RSE) Worker Training Programme will provide training in English language, computer skills, numeracy and financial literacy to1700 Pacific RSE workers annually in the Bay of Plenty, Hawkes Bay, Nelson, Marlborough, Northland, Waikato, Wairarapa and Central Otago.
